80
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:58,780
Thank you.

81
00:05:09,900 --> 00:05:10,980
You are really something.

82
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:11,940
It turned out

83
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,180
Ji Junxing really is a little rabbit.

84
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:15,740
