168
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:22,780
I'm not done yet.

169
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,660
The Art Class despises Class One.

170
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:29,540
No way.

171
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:32,180
I need to figure something out.

172
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,940
