I sprained my ankle.

687
00:34:12,580 --> 00:34:13,020
I'm fine.

688
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:15,100
No. You won't be able to keep playing.

689
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:16,100
Go to the infirmary now.

690
00:34:17,060 --> 00:34:17,500
Careful.

