00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:42,900
Just resign to your fate.

705
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:43,780
Moreover,

706
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:45,300
you have already done

707
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,460
a pretty good job.

